  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132410/extras/ccefd703789ebb3771d53b012f650810.avif?t=1575673502\" width=480 height=64 /></span><br><br><i>Cyber OutRun is an arcade pursuit game, inspired 80's aesthetic of neon lights and soundtracks.<br><br>The game offers you three game modes in a beautiful retro-futuristic visual atmosphere with Synthwave soundtrack.<br><br>Break law with your exotic car. Just turn on your radio and put the pedal to the metal, laws can't stop you!</i><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132410/extras/abdd0e5b334df2d77f0fa6a5583c74ad.avif?t=1575673502\" width=480 height=64 /></span><br><br><i>Cyber OutRun offers you three single player game modes</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132410/extras/46204bbbf7e4a5888ee27b8477decbc7.avif?t=1575673502\" width=128 height=98 /></span><br><strong>Reach highest heat level and avoid getting arrested.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132410/extras/ed32d9dafa407a339589cd8eff777c3b.avif?t=1575673502\" width=128 height=98 /></span><br><strong>Play against the clock and beat the time.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1132410/extras/1e73d7d1a5c0c7fa00a2195edad797ce.avif?t=1575673502\" width=128 height=98 /></span><br><strong>Drive free as the wind.</strong>",
